    public abstract class SystemOptionWithAssignmentBaseBL
extends SystemOptionBaseBL
    Base class for configuring the lists Contains the methods for configuring the list entries (insert, update, delete etc.) This class abstracts the list type i.e. these methods have the same signature independent of the select type: simple select, tree select, cascading select
